1. Take credit and movie data and merge them. 
2. Then remove null values. 
3. Apply data preprocessing to it. 
4. Convert the text data into numbers using vectorization.
5. Create an app using Streamlit.
6. Streamlit is an open-source Python library that allows you to build interactive web applications for data science and machine learning projects.
7. Using Pickle library, import the recommender file into pycharm to make an app.
